Meawm_NG uses automake, in order to generate the Makefiles for meawm_ng use:

	$ autogen.sh

After that, standard build procedures apply:

	$ make
	$ make install

For user specific configuration, copy and edit the following files:

	$ cp data/meawm_ngrc ~/.meawm_ngrc
	$ mkdir ~/.meawm_ng
	$ cp data/pre-action.conf ~/.meawm_ng
	$ cp data/pre-style.conf ~/.meawm_ng
	$ cp data/post-action.conf ~/.meawm_ng
	$ cp data/post-style.conf ~/.meawm_ng
